-- Volkswagen May Use Maruti Design, Factory Facilities in India, ET Reports
-- B y   S u p r o t i p   G h o s h
-- 2010-09-22T01:57:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-22/volkswagen-may-use-maruti-design-factory-facilities-in-india-et-reports.html
German carmaker Volkswagen AG may
extend its global partnership with Suzuki Motor Corp. in India
by tapping the manufacturing and design facilities of Maruti
Suzuki India Ltd., the Economic Times reported, quoting two
people familiar with the development.  To contact the reporter on this story:
